high_descs: Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the far side of the kitchen island.
Pick up the butter knife that is closest to the tomato on the kitchen island.
Turn around and walk over to the sink.
Put the butter knife in the glass that is in the sink.
Pick up the glass with the butter knife in it out of the sink.
Walk back over to the kitchen island behind you.
Put the glass with the butter knife in it on the island to the right of the plate.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a butter knife in it on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the wall,, then head left and once you pass the kitchen island, turn left again and stop so you're facing the gold plate on the island.
Pick up the butter knife closest to the tomato.
Turn around and carry the butter knife to the sink.
Place the knife in the martini glass.
Pick up the glass with the knife inside from the sink.
Turn back around to face the island again.
Place the glass with the knife in it on the island to the right of the gold plate.
anns.task_desc: Move a martini glass beneath a knife on the island.

high_descs: Turn around then left and face the table to your left.
Take the knife off the table in front of you.
Turn around and face the sink in front of you.
Place the knife in the glass in the sink in front of you.
Take the glass with the knife in the sink in front of you.
Turn around and face the table in front of you.
Place the glass on the table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass with a knife on the table.
